---
title: 'Go Fish!' Pie
description: We've added a twist to this simple fish pie by using leeks and sweet butternut squash! We've also added a little something special to make this dish extra fishy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/go-fish-pie-8a9ad0a5.jpg
